txt.en: Uiliúr can be found somewhere in the Ghâshghurm.\n\nYou should awake and defeat Uiliúr.
You have slain Uiliúr and vanquished a threat to the safety of all those who brave Mordor.

In disrupting the various forces gathered in Gorgoroth, a Caerog has risen out of the lava lake of Ghâshghurm. You should defeat this evil before someone else finds it and Uiliúr regains its full strength.
